    "notes": "An amazing long espresso for light roasts, this is the biggest fruit bomb of any brewing method we know.  5:1 ratio, 35-40 seconds, coarse espresso grind. If close to the right pressure, make 0.5g dose adjustments to get to an 8-9 bar peak. The very high flow rate means small grind adjustments cause big pressure changes. An advanced technique, allong\u00e9 averages 24% extraction.",
